{
  "name": "huawei-2025",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "analyzer.json - reads the CommonResults.txt and analyze all the commands to create json structured file inside output folder\r export_to_excel - reads the all json files from output folder and creates their excel versions in same output folder",
  "main": "main.js",
  "dependencies": {
    "adler-32": "^1.3.1",
    "buffer-from": "^1.1.2",
    "cfb": "^1.2.2",
    "codepage": "^1.15.0",
    "colors": "^0.6.2",
    "commander": "^14.0.1",
    "concat-stream": "^2.0.0",
    "crc-32": "^1.2.2",
    "frac": "^1.1.2",
    "inherits": "^2.0.4",
    "jszip": "^2.4.0",
    "pako": "^0.2.9",
    "readable-stream": "^3.6.2",
    "safe-buffer": "^5.2.1",
    "ssf": "^0.11.2",
    "string_decoder": "^1.3.0",
    "typedarray": "^0.0.6",
    "util-deprecate": "^1.0.2",
    "voc": "^1.2.0",
    "wmf": "^1.0.2",
    "word": "^0.3.0",
    "xlsx": "^0.18.5",
    "xlsx-style": "^0.8.13"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "electron": "^38.4.0",
    "electron-builder": "^24.13.3"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
    "start": "electron .",
    "build": "electron-builder --win --x64",
    "dist": "electron-builder --win"
  },
  "build": {
    "appId": "com.huawei2025.analyzer",
    "productName": "Huawei Log Analyzer",
    "directories": {
      "output": "dist"
    },
    "files": [
      "**/*",
      "!**/node_modules/*/{CHANGELOG.md,README.md,README,readme.md,readme}",
      "!**/node_modules/*/{test,__tests__,tests,powered-test,example,examples}",
      "!**/node_modules/*.d.ts",
      "!**/node_modules/.bin",
      "!**/*.{iml,o,hprof,orig,pyc,pyo,rbc,swp,csproj,sln,xproj}",
      "!.editorconfig",
      "!**/._*",
      "!**/{.DS_Store,.git,.hg,.svn,CVS,RCS,SCCS,.gitignore,.gitattributes}",
      "!**/{__pycache__,thumbs.db,.flowconfig,.idea,.vs,.nyc_output}",
      "!**/{appveyor.yml,.travis.yml,circle.yml}",
      "!**/{npm-debug.log,yarn.lock,.yarn-integrity,.yarn-metadata.json}"
    ],
    "win": {
      "icon": "build/icon.ico",
      "target": [
        {
          "target": "nsis",
          "arch": ["x64"]
        },
        {
          "target": "portable",
          "arch": ["x64"]
        }
      ]
    },
    "nsis": {
      "oneClick": false,
      "allowToChangeInstallationDirectory": true,
      "createDesktopShortcut": true,
      "createStartMenuShortcut": true
    }
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/AlexsorBlog/Huawei-2025.git"
  },
  "keywords": [],
  "author": "",
  "license": "ISC",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/AlexsorBlog/Huawei-2025/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/AlexsorBlog/Huawei-2025#readme"
}
